## node_done 输出格式要求
当输出 ACTION: node_done 时，node_output 必须严格包含以下字段：
```json
{"action": "node_done", "node_output": {
  "execution_results": [
    {"task_id": "task_1", "task_type": "legal_query", "description": "查询描述", "status": "completed", "result": "查询结果"}
  ]
}, "thought": "..."}
```
execution_results 是必
